1
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:39,300
"Kontras"

2
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:42,700
(Episod 4: Hanya Berpura-pura Tidur)

3
00:01:42,780 --> 00:01:44,540
Apa yang dia cuba buat tadi?

4
00:01:45,890 --> 00:01:46,890
Akira...

5
00:01:51,830 --> 00:01:52,830
ciuman?

6
00:01:55,323 --> 00:01:56,323
Tidak, saya...

7
00:01:57,910 --> 00:01:58,910
Tetapi...

8
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:00,580
Bukan itu maksudnya...

9
00:02:44,060 --> 00:02:45,700
Oh, Akira, awak dah siapkan tugasan?

10
00:02:45,850 --> 00:02:47,150
Ya, saya sudah selesai.

11
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,160
Itu adalah pantas.

12
00:02:48,610 --> 00:02:49,810
Anda belum selesai lagi?

13
00:02:49,820 --> 00:02:51,660
Tidak mungkin saya boleh
habiskan secepat itu.

14
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:53,850
Wah, itu sudah dekat...

15
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:56,750
Awak okay?

16
00:02:59,170 --> 00:03:00,610
Perhatikan ke mana anda pergi.

17
00:03:02,980 --> 00:03:03,980
Ya.

18
00:03:18,650 --> 00:03:20,430
Saya sangat mengidam ini.

19
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:23,120
Dan mereka berada di luar kebiasaan saya
roti bacon hari ini.

20
00:03:23,430 --> 00:03:24,710
Apakah jenis roti itu?

21
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,959
Jom, saya dapat roti kari juga.

22
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:28,519
- Roti kari lagi? Dengan jus epal?
- Saya mempunyai roti kari setiap hari.

23
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,520
Saya sangat muak dengannya.

24
00:03:30,130 --> 00:03:31,130
apa khabar?

25
00:03:31,310 --> 00:03:32,310
Hmm?

26
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:33,480
Bukan apa.

27
00:03:34,060 --> 00:03:37,290
Anda hanya berharap seorang gadis comel
akan datang mengaku kepada anda, bukan?

28
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:39,260
- Betul ke?
- Hei, di mana? Di mana dia?

29
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:40,640
bukan itu sahaja.

30
00:03:40,860 --> 00:03:42,500
Makki, jom.

31
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:44,050
Jumpa, Kanata.

32
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,680
- Awak ketagih roti kari tu.
- Hei, tunggu!

33
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:08,310
Hei, dengan cara ini...

34
00:04:08,410 --> 00:04:11,020
Pada masa itu, tidak
muka kita... rapat sangat ke?

35
00:04:12,490 --> 00:04:13,490
Tidak, tunggu...

36
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,380
ciuman.

37
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:02,700
Adakah anda cuba mencium saya?

38
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,280
Hah?

39
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,120
Saya tahu ia.

40
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:10,840
Awak berpura-pura tidur.

41
00:05:11,750 --> 00:05:12,850
apa yang awak cakap ni?

42
00:05:14,140 --> 00:05:15,790
Tak kisahlah.

43
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:19,430
Bagaimanapun...

44
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:22,070
Awak bukan jenis sebenarnya
untuk membuat lawak seperti itu, Akira.

45
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,590
macam mana?

46
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:26,290
Bagaimana saya boleh meletakkannya...

47
00:05:29,310 --> 00:05:31,520
Anda tidak kelihatan seperti itu
menaip untuk bercakap tentang perkara yang kotor.

48
00:05:32,980 --> 00:05:33,980
Tidak juga.

49
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:35,830
Saya bercakap mengenainya.

50
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,780
dengan siapa?

51
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:41,520
Awak tanya saya dengan siapa...

52
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,500
(Kanda Yoichi: Masa biasa?)

53
00:05:48,250 --> 00:05:49,550
Siapa Kanda?

54
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,900
Kawan abang.

55
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,340
Awak ada abang?

56
00:05:55,590 --> 00:05:56,590
Berapa umur dia?

57
00:05:58,330 --> 00:06:00,020
Sekitar 23, saya fikir.

58
00:06:01,650 --> 00:06:02,650
Tunggu, jangan beritahu saya...

59
00:06:03,100 --> 00:06:04,970
Anda bercakap tentang perkara kotor dengan orang dewasa?

60
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,640
Saya rasa begitu.

61
00:06:09,230 --> 00:06:11,000
Tunggu, Akira, adakah awak...?

62
00:06:14,496 --> 00:06:17,336
Oh... tak kisahlah.

63
00:06:17,370 --> 00:06:18,120
Tiada komen.

64
00:06:18,121 --> 00:06:19,620
Ah, jangan cakap apa-apa.

65
00:06:19,910 --> 00:06:21,110
Anda tidak perlu mengatakannya.

66
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:23,210
Saya tidak memberi anda jawapan pun.

67
00:06:24,610 --> 00:06:26,190
Oh, betul...

68
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:27,960
Saya rasa begitu...

69
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:29,630
Ya.

70
00:06:32,970 --> 00:06:34,170
Saya rasa macam...

71
00:06:35,330 --> 00:06:37,600
masih banyak saya
tidak tahu tentang awak.

72
00:06:43,410 --> 00:06:44,510
Ya.

73
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:50,850
Kelas solek memang memenatkan.

74
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:52,680
Kerja bagus.

75
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:53,950
Mahu berjalan pulang bersama-sama?
pasti.

76
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:58,910
Dia betul-betul bekerja keras.

77
00:06:58,980 --> 00:06:59,980
Ya.

78
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:02,770
Rentak kompetitif itu
dia tidak berubah.

79
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,360
Mm-hmm.

80
00:07:05,380 --> 00:07:06,660
Tapi saya rasa macam...

81
00:07:07,190 --> 00:07:08,190
dia agak lain sekarang.

82
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:09,630
Oh?

83
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:10,930
Cuma...

84
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:13,690
Bagaimana saya mengatakannya? dia
mula tersenyum sebenarnya.

85
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:15,940
Ya.

86
00:07:17,180 --> 00:07:18,410
Oh, lusa...

87
00:07:18,820 --> 00:07:20,549
Saya akan pergi lewat malam
filem dengan Kanata.

88
00:07:20,550 --> 00:07:21,566
Mizuki, awak nak ikut ke?

89
00:07:21,590 --> 00:07:22,590
Oh, saya suka.

90
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:24,739
OK, saya akan menempah tempat duduk kemudian.

91
00:07:24,740 --> 00:07:25,930
Terima kasih.

92
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:55,430
By the way...

93
00:07:55,431 --> 00:07:57,650
Bagaimana keadaan Hikaru kebelakangan ini?

94
00:07:58,880 --> 00:07:59,880
Oh...

95
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:00,920
abang saya?

96
00:08:00,921 --> 00:08:03,450
Dia kelihatan baik apabila kami
bercakap di telefon baru-baru ini.

97
00:08:04,890 --> 00:08:05,890
saya nampak.

98
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,030
Anda tidak terus berhubung?

99
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:12,680
Tidak seperti dulu.

100
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:18,280
Oh, ia tidak seperti kita dalam keadaan yang buruk.

101
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,240
Cuma saya sedang bekerja...

102
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,810
dan dia masih di sekolah ijazah.

103
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,680
Kami secara semula jadi kurang bercakap.

104
00:08:26,110 --> 00:08:27,110
Betul.

105
00:08:29,290 --> 00:08:31,610
Sukar untuk percaya betapa rapatnya kami dahulu.

106
00:08:41,050 --> 00:08:42,050
saya dah balik.

107
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,400
maafkan saya.

108
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:46,030
Lelaki ini adalah tutor anda.

109
00:08:47,130 --> 00:08:48,410
Tutor?

110
00:08:48,470 --> 00:08:50,430
Ya, kawan dari sekolah menengah.

111
00:08:50,710 --> 00:08:52,330
Dia sudah banyak kali ke rumah kami.

112
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:56,540
Saya fikir anda berkata anda akan berhenti
sesak sekolah sebelum musim panas...

113
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:59,630
Yoichi sedang mencari sambilan
pekerjaan, jadi saya fikir ia akan menjadi sempurna.

114
00:08:59,890 --> 00:09:01,820
Lagipun, peperiksaan kemasukan adalah penting.

115
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:03,760
Jika awak okay dengannya, Akira.

116
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:06,800
Saya...

117
00:09:07,460 --> 00:09:08,660
Saya akan menghargainya.

118
00:09:09,140 --> 00:09:10,140
bagus.

119
00:09:11,090 --> 00:09:12,530
Tidak sabar untuk bekerja dengan anda.

120
00:09:27,350 --> 00:09:29,490
Adakah anda suka muzik juga, Akira?

121
00:09:31,470 --> 00:09:33,990
Saya... tidak tahu sangat mengenainya.

122
00:09:35,330 --> 00:09:36,530
saya nampak.

123
00:09:38,196 --> 00:09:39,706
Abang saya yang terlibat.

124
00:09:40,820 --> 00:09:42,210
Dia mendengar perkara yang benar-benar bergaya.

125
00:09:44,210 --> 00:09:45,410
Jika anda mendengar...

126
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:47,680
adakah jenis muzik tertentu yang anda suka?

127
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:50,960
Hmm...

128
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:53,110
Mungkin sesuatu yang kuat.

129
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:55,100
Kuat?

130
00:09:56,110 --> 00:09:57,110
Suka...

131
00:09:57,190 --> 00:09:58,520
sesuatu yang terasa katartik.

132
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:01,020
Sesuatu di mana...

133
00:10:01,830 --> 00:10:04,030
anda tidak perlu berfikir
tentang apa sahaja semasa mendengar.

134
00:10:04,570 --> 00:10:07,280
Dalam kes itu, saya mempunyai beberapa cadangan.

135
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,340
Mereka band asing.

136
00:10:09,490 --> 00:10:11,230
Saya mempunyai CD. Saya akan bawa mereka lain kali.

137
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,590
Terima kasih.

138
00:10:16,460 --> 00:10:18,889
Hikaru nampaknya tidak begitu menyukai gaya ini.

139
00:10:18,890 --> 00:10:20,399
Apabila kumpulan itu datang ke Jepun...

140
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:22,270
Saya akhirnya pergi sendiri.

141
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:25,110
Oh, tetapi kami pergi ke a
pesta muzik bersama.

142
00:10:26,580 --> 00:10:27,780
You guys are really close.

143
00:10:28,850 --> 00:10:30,210
Sejak abang balik...

144
00:10:30,430 --> 00:10:31,530
dia sentiasa ada dengan awak.

145
00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:35,460
Dia berada di Kansai sekarang, jadi
susah nak jumpa.

146
00:10:37,770 --> 00:10:39,610
Kami tidak sama
kelas di sekolah menengah...

147
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:43,240
tapi saya ingat tertanya-tanya
yang mendapat gred lebih baik daripada saya.

148
00:10:43,340 --> 00:10:44,820
Ternyata itu dia.

149
00:10:45,350 --> 00:10:46,910
Anda berdua cukup menakjubkan.

150
00:10:47,790 --> 00:10:49,510
Tetapi gred awak juga bagus, kan, Akira?

151
00:10:51,060 --> 00:10:52,450
Mereka okey.

152
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:56,640
Tetapi saya tidak pernah mendapat tempat teratas dalam kelas.

153
00:10:57,100 --> 00:10:58,950
Hei, itu masih mengagumkan.

154
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:02,680
Nah... saya rasa.

155
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:08,860
Berbanding abang...

156
00:11:10,460 --> 00:11:11,980
Saya benar-benar tidak boleh mengalahkan dia dalam apa-apa pun.

157
00:11:17,730 --> 00:11:20,070
Adakah anda berasa rendah diri?

158
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:34,310
Jika ada hari anda tidak perlu
kekalkan keseimbangan itu, pastikan anda memberitahu saya.

159
00:11:41,050 --> 00:11:42,050
Okey...

160
00:11:47,860 --> 00:11:49,669
Ayuh, beritahu saya.

161
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:51,136
Anda sebenarnya mempunyai teman wanita, bukan?

162
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,240
Dia pergi sekolah mana?

163
00:11:53,100 --> 00:11:55,290
Saya tidak pasti sama ada saya akan menelefon
ia "menyukai" seseorang...

164
00:11:56,540 --> 00:11:59,240
tetapi ada seseorang
siapa yang rasa macam tu?

165
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:10,520
Senkawa-kun.

166
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:13,020
Terima kasih untuk hari yang lain.

167
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:14,610
Mengenai Kanata.

168
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:17,170
Oh... saya tak buat banyak sangat.

169
00:12:17,940 --> 00:12:21,090
Saya rasa Kanata telah berubah
sejak dia jumpa awak.

170
00:12:21,390 --> 00:12:22,390
Hah?

171
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:25,230
Seolah-olah dia kembali seperti dulu
apabila dia mengambil serius bola sepak.

172
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,020
Saya sangat gembira mengenainya.

173
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:30,680
saya nampak.

174
00:12:32,310 --> 00:12:33,310
Jadi...

175
00:12:33,311 --> 00:12:34,560
terima kasih, sungguh.

176
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:36,640
pasti.

177
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:37,660
Jika anda tidak keberatan...

178
00:12:37,661 --> 00:12:39,141
mahu berjalan ke stesen bersama-sama?

179
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,880
Oh, okay.

180
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:49,920
Senkawa-kun.

181
00:12:49,980 --> 00:12:51,650
Adakah anda belajar lebih banyak selepas sekolah menjejalkan?

182
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:53,160
Hah?

183
00:12:53,230 --> 00:12:55,700
Orang yang kita jumpa...
bukankah awak kata dia tutor awak?

184
00:12:56,370 --> 00:12:57,370
Oh...

185
00:12:58,610 --> 00:13:00,140
Dia tutor saya, tapi...

186
00:13:00,610 --> 00:13:02,170
dia sebenarnya kawan abang saya.

187
00:13:02,417 --> 00:13:04,957
saya nampak. Jadi awak ada abang.

188
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,270
Ya.

189
00:13:06,830 --> 00:13:08,570
Dia berada di universiti di Kyoto sekarang.

190
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:11,080
Oh, Kyoto.

191
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:14,470
itu bagus. Saya tidak pernah ke sana.

192
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,040
Um...

193
00:13:19,950 --> 00:13:20,950
ya?

194
00:13:21,290 --> 00:13:23,820
Ada sesuatu yang saya ingin tanya.

195
00:13:24,310 --> 00:13:25,310
Apa itu?

196
00:13:26,660 --> 00:13:27,960
Kanata...

197
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:29,750
Hmm?

198
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:36,760
Maaf.

199
00:13:36,930 --> 00:13:37,930
Tak kisahlah.

200
00:13:56,610 --> 00:13:57,610
Yo.

201
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,360
Selamat bekerja hari ini.

202
00:14:03,850 --> 00:14:04,850
Ah...

203
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,080
Otot saya membunuh saya.

204
00:14:08,110 --> 00:14:09,110
Apa khabar kelab?

205
00:14:09,740 --> 00:14:10,740
Bagaimana keadaannya?

206
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:12,560
Tidak mengapa.

207
00:14:14,220 --> 00:14:15,220
Adakah anda berseronok?

208
00:14:16,700 --> 00:14:17,700
Ya.

209
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,720
Maksud saya, saya...

210
00:14:20,420 --> 00:14:21,840
tetapi ia adalah rumit.

211
00:14:23,490 --> 00:14:26,050
Kami tidak berjaya melepasinya
peringkat awal untuk kejohanan seterusnya.

212
00:14:27,210 --> 00:14:28,619
Tetapi saya hanya orang baru...

213
00:14:28,620 --> 00:14:30,400
jadi saya tidak berhak untuk mengadu.

214
00:14:31,970 --> 00:14:32,970
saya nampak.

215
00:14:33,410 --> 00:14:36,140
Oh, tetapi ada beberapa
mengejutkan lelaki yang baik.

216
00:14:36,570 --> 00:14:38,290
Tahun depan mesti lebih menarik.

217
00:14:40,700 --> 00:14:42,000
Saya rasa itu kedengaran agak sombong.

218
00:14:43,410 --> 00:14:46,360
Saya gembira anda dapat bermain.

219
00:14:48,140 --> 00:14:49,140
Ya.

220
00:15:04,290 --> 00:15:05,290
mengantuk?

221
00:15:05,830 --> 00:15:06,830
Ya.

222
00:15:07,770 --> 00:15:10,230
Anggaplah ia sebagai ganjaran kerana bekerja keras.

223
00:15:13,530 --> 00:15:14,690
Apa maksudnya?

224
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,600
Hei.

225
00:15:35,860 --> 00:15:36,860
Hmm?

226
00:15:45,450 --> 00:15:46,450
Akira...

227
00:15:51,550 --> 00:15:52,920
Adakah anda pernah mencium sesiapa?

228
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,240
Bagaimana dengan awak, Kanata?

229
00:15:59,490 --> 00:16:00,490
Ah.

230
00:16:01,260 --> 00:16:02,260
Itu tidak adil.

231
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:03,700
saya tanya dulu.

232
00:16:07,260 --> 00:16:08,260
saya ada.

233
00:16:10,780 --> 00:16:11,780
awak?

234
00:16:20,890 --> 00:16:21,890
Saya juga.

235
00:16:31,510 --> 00:16:32,710
Seseorang yang anda dating?

236
00:16:35,060 --> 00:16:36,060
Tidak.

237
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:38,680
Seseorang yang anda suka?

238
00:16:42,700 --> 00:16:43,700
Siapa tahu...

239
00:16:44,290 --> 00:16:45,850
apa? Itu sangat samar.

240
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,200
Bagaimana dengan awak?

241
00:16:52,070 --> 00:16:53,070
Saya...

242
00:16:56,610 --> 00:16:58,000
Seperti yang saya katakan sebelum ini...

243
00:16:58,970 --> 00:17:00,410
Saya tidak mengambil berat tentang apa-apa.

244
00:17:02,140 --> 00:17:04,060
Asalkan saya ada sesuatu
lakukan selain bola sepak.

245
00:17:06,410 --> 00:17:11,250
Jadi... saya cuma main-main.

246
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:13,540
Hanya untuk mengalih perhatian saya.

247
00:17:19,870 --> 00:17:21,070
Adakah awak memandang rendah saya?

248
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:24,280
Tidak.

249
00:17:26,830 --> 00:17:27,830
saya nampak.

250
00:17:29,660 --> 00:17:31,620
Saya fikir anda akan lebih
serius tentang perkara itu.

251
00:17:33,550 --> 00:17:34,770
Tetapi saya berbeza sekarang.

252
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:39,800
Oh.

253
00:17:41,490 --> 00:17:42,490
Tetapi...

254
00:17:43,606 --> 00:17:45,275
Awak tahu saya berpura-pura tidur...

255
00:17:45,300 --> 00:17:46,620
dan awak masih berbuat demikian pada saya.

256
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:48,600
Hah?

257
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:51,200
Di hari raya.

258
00:17:51,470 --> 00:17:53,070
Awak dekat muka saya.

259
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:55,100
Oh...

260
00:17:55,990 --> 00:17:56,990
Maaf.

261
00:17:57,370 --> 00:17:58,570
Berhenti mengacau saya.

262
00:18:02,220 --> 00:18:03,260
Saya tidak main-main dengan awak.

263
00:18:05,460 --> 00:18:06,460
Cuma...

264
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,820
Saya sedikit cemburu dengan awak.

265
00:18:11,020 --> 00:18:12,220
apa maksud awak?

266
00:18:14,780 --> 00:18:16,320
Saya fikir jika saya lebih dekat dengan awak...

267
00:18:18,250 --> 00:18:19,830
mungkin saya boleh menjadi lebih seperti awak.

268
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:22,660
Awak nak jadi macam saya?

269
00:18:23,350 --> 00:18:24,990
Lebih baik tidak. Gred anda akan meningkat.

270
00:18:26,900 --> 00:18:28,810
Walaupun anda akan menjadi lebih baik dalam bola sepak.

271
00:18:30,300 --> 00:18:31,500
betul.

272
00:18:32,770 --> 00:18:36,300
Tapi bahagian gred sikit...

273
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:40,410
Kami berbeza, dan
itu satu perkara yang baik, bukan?

274
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:44,069
Lagipun, walaupun kita dah dekat macam tu...

275
00:18:44,070 --> 00:18:46,010
ia tidak akan membuatkan anda menjadi seperti saya.

276
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:49,420
awak betul.

277
00:18:51,790 --> 00:18:53,470
Anda menukar topik, bukan?

278
00:19:02,460 --> 00:19:05,380
Adakah itu tidak dibenarkan?

279
00:19:10,950 --> 00:19:11,950
Tidak.

280
00:19:16,470 --> 00:19:20,580
Kali ini... anda sepatutnya
berpura-pura tidur juga.

281
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:10,000
Sial, saya perlu pergi.

282
00:20:11,220 --> 00:20:12,889
Hei, kita semua pergi menonton wayang hari ini.

283
00:20:12,890 --> 00:20:13,890
Awak nak ikut, Akira?

284
00:20:15,070 --> 00:20:15,900
Maaf.

285
00:20:15,901 --> 00:20:17,661
- Saya berjumpa dengan abang saya hari ini...
- Oh, saya faham.

286
00:20:17,770 --> 00:20:18,770
Jumpa lagi lain kali.

287
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,440
apa salahnya

288
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:36,160
Hah?

289
00:20:37,380 --> 00:20:38,930
Muka awak merah padam.

290
00:20:40,850 --> 00:20:41,850
Saya hampir lewat.

291
00:20:42,050 --> 00:20:43,050
Itulah sebabnya saya berlari.

292
00:20:57,180 --> 00:20:58,180
Okay.

293
00:20:58,650 --> 00:20:59,850
Sekarang kemudian.

294
00:20:59,920 --> 00:21:02,950
Puisi ini menggambarkan kegembiraan
melihat orang tersayang dalam mimpi...

295
00:21:03,090 --> 00:21:06,470
dan kesedihan apabila bangun.

296
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:12,690
Ingin melihat orang itu
awak sayang, walaupun dalam mimpi...

297
00:21:13,520 --> 00:21:15,079
Untuk mengambil berat seseorang itu...

298
00:21:15,080 --> 00:21:16,640
sebenarnya adalah sesuatu yang indah.

299
00:21:25,060 --> 00:21:26,850
Maaf saya lambat.

300
00:21:26,940 --> 00:21:27,640
Jangan risau.

301
00:21:27,700 --> 00:21:29,420
Saya hanya membunuh masa
sekitar sini pula.

302
00:21:30,490 --> 00:21:31,490
By the way, mana Jun?

303
00:21:31,590 --> 00:21:33,520
Oh, dia mesej mengatakan dia akan lewat sedikit.

304
00:21:33,990 --> 00:21:36,000
Dan dia yang mendesak kita pergi hari ini.

305
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:38,470
Oh.

306
00:21:38,490 --> 00:21:40,210
Patutkah kita lihat jika Senkawa-kun mahu menyertainya?

307
00:21:40,700 --> 00:21:42,026
Kalau dia baru habis sekolah cram...

308
00:21:42,050 --> 00:21:43,459
dia sepatutnya masih ada di sini.

309
00:21:43,460 --> 00:21:44,460
tak perlu.

310
00:21:47,550 --> 00:21:49,200
Dia ada rancangan hari ini.

311
00:21:49,820 --> 00:21:51,169
Sesuatu dengan abangnya.

312
00:21:51,170 --> 00:21:52,170
Hah?

313
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:54,100
Saya dengar Akira ada abang.

314
00:21:54,610 --> 00:21:56,160
Ya, saya tahu.

315
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:58,560
Kami bercakap mengenainya di
jalan balik dari sekolah cram.

316
00:21:58,800 --> 00:21:59,960
Oh, betul ke?

317
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:01,760
Tetapi...

318
00:22:01,900 --> 00:22:04,980
Saya dengar abangnya
di universiti di Kyoto.

319
00:22:05,670 --> 00:22:06,670
Tunggu, apa?

320
00:22:07,370 --> 00:22:10,370
Maksud saya, mungkin dia kembali untuk melawat.

321
00:22:12,270 --> 00:22:13,270
saya rasa.

322
00:22:16,060 --> 00:22:17,420
Bagaimana saya boleh meletakkan ini...

323
00:22:36,220 --> 00:22:37,220
Akira...?

324
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:28,896
(Episod Seterusnya)
Jom buat kem latihan.

325
00:23:28,920 --> 00:23:30,450
Adakah anda cuba untuk belajar?

326
00:23:31,030 --> 00:23:32,030
Wah, menakjubkan.

327
00:23:32,600 --> 00:23:34,200
Tunggu, hanya saya yang mempunyai brek!

328
00:23:37,720 --> 00:23:38,720
Kanata.

329
00:23:38,850 --> 00:23:40,240
Kenapa awak cium saya?

